{"id":11088,"date":"2024-03-17T16:11:47","date_gmt":"2024-03-17T09:11:47","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=11088"},"modified":"2024-03-17T16:31:18","modified_gmt":"2024-03-17T09:31:18","slug":"phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu\/","title":{"rendered":"Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c, ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Trong th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n, ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua b\u00e1n c\u0103n h\u1ed9. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b><i>Vinhomeland<\/i><\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0, m\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua trong th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n ng\u00e0y nay.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n sang ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua. Chi ph\u00ed n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb giao d\u1ecbch v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i tu\u00e2n theo c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt ho\u1eb7c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 ph\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u00e0 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11089\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11089\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11089 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-1.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11089\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11089\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-1.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11089\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua chung c\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu chi ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi chuy\u1ec3n quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 do b\u00ean n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed9t kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh quan tr\u1ecdng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n. C\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn thanh to\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ph\u00ed:<\/strong> Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m thanh to\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn thanh to\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n ph\u00ed:<\/strong> Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cam k\u1ebft ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m thanh to\u00e1n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ho\u1eb7c m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m cho giao d\u1ecbch tr\u1edf n\u00ean thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd k\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ecdc v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh hi\u1ec3u l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn sau n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11090\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11090\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11090 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-2.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/500;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11090\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11090\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-2.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11090\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh giao d\u1ecbch tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ee7i ro. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra v\u00e0 n\u1eafm v\u1eefng c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean quan, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed ph\u00e1t sinh. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i kh\u00f4ng mong mu\u1ed1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 10 ng\u00e0y t\u00ednh t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u l\u1ef1c. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec7 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 khai thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u00e1n nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u00ednh to\u00e1n thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u1ea7n n\u1ed9p theo c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b><i>Thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p = Gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng x 2%<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n nh\u00e0: Chi ph\u00ed n\u00e0y dao \u0111\u1ed9ng trong kho\u1ea3ng 4 \u2013 5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0: ph\u00ed in \u1ea5n, l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed, chi ph\u00ed cho c\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng vi\u00ean,\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi: Chi ph\u00ed n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb 1 \u2013 2% c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 cho ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p t\u00ednh ph\u00ed, m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed th\u01b0\u1eddng dao \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 3 \u2013 5 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u1ea7n thanh to\u00e1n m\u1ed9t ph\u00ed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 khai l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed k\u00e8m theo khi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u00e1 mua b\u00e1n chung c\u01b0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a UBND c\u1ea5p t\u1ec9nh:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b><i>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 = 0,5% x Gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu gi\u00e1 mua b\u00e1n chung c\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n m\u1ee9c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a UBND c\u1ea5p t\u1ec9nh:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b><i>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 = 0,5% x (Di\u1ec7n t\u00edch x Gi\u00e1\/1m2 x T\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 (%) ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i)<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11091\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11091\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11091 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-3.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/500;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11091\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11091\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-3.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11091\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Giao d\u1ecbch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ee7i ro cao h\u01a1n.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n giao d\u1ecbch c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng chi ph\u00ed v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p. C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ebf c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p bao g\u1ed3m thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh mua b\u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng. Vi\u1ec7c n\u1eafm v\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n trong giao d\u1ecbch mua b\u00e1n l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn thu\u1ebf trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ebf c\u1ea7n n\u1ed9p<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi mua b\u00e1n<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean thu nh\u1eadp t\u00ednh thu\u1ebf, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0110i\u1ec1u 20 Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh 65\/2013\/N\u0110-CP, c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b><i>Thu nh\u1eadp t\u00ednh thu\u1ebf = (Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n) \u2013 (gi\u00e1 mua) \u2013 (c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan)<\/i><\/b><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ecdi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ecbu thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n khi mua b\u00e1n. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n n\u1ed9p thu\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u00e1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u0103n chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 b\u1ec7nh t\u1eadt, h\u1ecfa ho\u1ea1n, ho\u1eb7c thi\u00ean tai, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m thu\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0, theo \u0110i\u1ec1u 22 Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh 65\/2013\/N\u0110-CP (\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung b\u1edfi Kho\u1ea3n 12 Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh 12\/2015\/N\u0110-CP), bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 2% tr\u00ean gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eb7ng<\/span><\/strong><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eb7ng, thu\u1ebf thu nh\u1eadp c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh cho b\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mua b\u00e1n, d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng (\u0110i\u1ec1u 23 Ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ecbnh 65\/2013\/N\u0110-CP).<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3m thu\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 khi mua b\u00e1n, bao g\u1ed3m gi\u1ea3m thu\u1ebf trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, mi\u1ec5n thu\u1ebf khi b\u00e1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh ho\u1eb7c khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 c\u0103n chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, thu\u1ebf su\u1ea5t s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh theo bi\u1ec3u thu\u1ebf to\u00e0n ph\u1ea7n v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c 10%.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_11092\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11092\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11092 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-4.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"618\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/618;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11092\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11092\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-4.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"618\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11092\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua l\u1eabn ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thanh to\u00e1n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i ph\u00ed v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf.<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee9c l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed c\u1ea7n n\u1ed9p<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed ch\u00ednh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1:<\/strong> C\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1eb1ng 0,5% c\u1ee7a gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thanh to\u00e1n b\u1edfi b\u00ean mua, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf:<\/strong> Ph\u00ed n\u00e0y c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb 50.000 \u0111\u1ebfn 100.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c:<\/strong> G\u1ed3m c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed nh\u01b0 ph\u00ed th\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn, ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ecba ch\u00ednh, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t sinh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_11093\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11093\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11093 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-5.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/500;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11093\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11093\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu-5.jpg\" alt=\"ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11093\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b><i>Vinhomeland<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u1ec1 <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/phi-chuyen-nhuong-chung-cu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0<\/b><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00e0 c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan, \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i cho c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e1n. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi giao d\u1ecbch, h\u00e3y nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh r\u1ee7i ro, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;11088&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;ignore&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reference&quot;:&quot;auto&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;count&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;legendonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;readonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;score&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;starsonly&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;best&quot;:&quot;5&quot;,&quot;gap&quot;:&quot;4&quot;,&quot;greet&quot;:&quot;\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft&quot;,&quot;legend&quot;:&quot;0\\\/5 - (0 b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;20&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c, ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t&quot;,&quot;width&quot;:&quot;0&quot;